				Um, a mage against a necro?  My money is on a necro.  First the pets engage, ok fine, my pet with say, sword of runes, which procs against his skelly.  So my pet is pummeling away at the skelly.  The necro is life and mana taping me whilst I nuke the skelly as you so ignorantly suggest.  Fine, skelly is dead, but now I am at 25% heath and no mana and the necro lifetaps my pet whilst he (necro) beats me over the head, and necro-nukes me.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
The whole fight would last say--30 sec?<BR>
One dead mage<BR>
<BR>
Necro are way more powerful than mages.  Get a clue, &quot;Truth.&quot;
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
